Charter Federal Savings Loan Association Bristol Va. agree acquire Jefferson Savings Loan Association Warrenton Va. Under term transaction result 1.3 billion dlr thrift institution stockholder Jefferson 30.50 dlrs share half cash half share Charter. The result association operate name Charter base Bristol. The transaction value 16.3 mln dlrs Jefferson spokesman said. Charter merger subject approval Federal Home Loan Bank Board. Jefferson report 1.5 mln dlrs loss asset 360 mln dlrs end September 30 1986. For end June 30 Charter report net income 7.9 mln dlrs. Assets total 844.0 mln dlrs December 31. Reuter 